            </div>
            <div class="step-connector">→</div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">03</div>
                <div class="step-icon">📱</div>
                <h3>Smart Control with DripSphere OS™</h3>
                <p>Monitor soil moisture, schedule irrigations, and run precision fertigation — all from your phone. Full visibility over every zone, every field.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-connector">→</div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">04</div>
                <div class="step-icon">📈</div>
                <h3>Watch Yields Climb</h3>
                <p>Crops get exactly what they need, when they need it. Less water waste, more nutrients retained, bigger harvests season after season.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
